flowchart TB
    IN[Order + seller context] --> FILT[Filter: hard constraints]
    FILT --> CAND[Surviving candidates]
    CAND --> RATE[Pricing engine: rates per candidate]
    CAND --> REL[Reliability scores per carrier x zone]
    RATE --> SCO[Compute weighted scores]
    REL --> SCO
    SCO --> RANK[Rank candidates]
    RANK --> EXP[Audit: filtered_out + scores + weights]
    RANK --> OUT[Recommended pick + ranked alternatives]
